title: Episode 35 - Raelene Boyle Interview (Brink Vault 2013)
itunes:title: Episode 35 - Raelene Boyle Interview (Brink Vault 2013)
description: Another legend of Australian Olympics today in our 'vault' series as we bring a chat from 2013 with the legendary Raelene Boyle. Talking up her role as part of the Breast Cancer Network of Australia as well as touching on her Olympic career, it's a chat you definitely won't want to miss.
